                        <interp inst="t18381022-name-595" type="given" value="HARRIET"></interp>HARRIET GOLDING</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Shadwell—I was at Mr. Levy'house, near Wellclose-square—I went into the area, and picked up a watch—my master gave it to the officer—this is it (<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>.)</p>
